.\" Manpage for simple_shell
.TH simple_shell 1 "December 2023" "1.0" "Simple Shell Manual"

.SH NAME
simple_shell \- a super simple shell program

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B simple_shell

.SH DESCRIPTION
.I simple_shell
is a basic interactive command-line shell that allows users to enter commands and execute them.

.SH OPTIONS
This program does not support any command-line options.

.SH USAGE
To run the simple shell, execute the following command in the terminal:
.PP
.EX
$ simple_shell
.EE

Once running, enter commands at the prompt (e.g., $ ls, $ echo "Hello").

.SH COMMANDS
The simple shell supports basic commands available on the system.
.TP
.B exit
Exit the shell.
.TP
.B [command]
Execute the specified command.

.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Successful program execution.
.TP
.B 1
An error occurred (e.g., invalid command, failure to execute).

.SH SEE ALSO
.BR exec (3)

.SH EXAMPLES
Execute a command:
.PP
.EX
$ simple_shell
$ ls
.EE
Exit the shell:
.PP
.EX
$ simple_shell
$ exit
.EE

.SH BUGS
No known bugs.

.SH AUTHOR
Gilles and Benjamin
